<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr" class="dark">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Sentinel Dashboard | v2.0.1-beta.1</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;600;700;800&display=swap');
        body { 
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            background-color: #0f172a; 
        }
        .card-glass {
            background: rgba(30, 41, 59, 0.7);
            backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
            transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
        }
        .card-glass:hover {
            border-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5);
            transform: translateY(-4px);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="text-slate-200 antialiased">

    <nav class="flex items-center justify-between px-6 py-4 bg-slate-900/80 sticky top-0 z-50 border-b border-slate-800 backdrop-blur-md">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
            <div class="relative">
                <img src="<%= bot.displayAvatarURL() %>" class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full border-2 border-blue-500 shadow-blue-500/20 shadow-lg">
                <div class="absolute bottom-0 right-0 w-3 h-3 bg-green-500 border-2 border-slate-900 rounded-full"></div>
            </div>
            <div>
                <span class="text-xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-white">Sentinel <span class="text-blue-500 text-sm font-mono ml-1">BETA</span></span>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="flex items-center gap-6">
            <div class="hidden md:flex flex-col items-end">
                <span class="text-xs font-mono text-green-400">STATUS: ONLINE</span>
                <span class="text-[10px] text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-widest">Render.com Instance</span>
            </div>
            <a href="/logout" class="bg-red-500/10 hover:bg-red-500 text-red-500 hover:text-white px-4 py-2 rounded-lg text-sm font-semibold transition-all border border-red-500/20">
                <i class="fas fa-sign-out-alt mr-2"></i>Déconnexion
            </a>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <main class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 py-12">
        
        <div class="mb-12">
            <h1 class="text-4xl font-black text-white tracking-tight italic">COMMAND CENTER</h1>
            <p class="text-slate-400 mt-2">Gestion globale de l'instance Sentinel v2.0.1-beta.1</p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6 mb-12">
            
            <div class="card-glass p-6 rounded-2xl">
                <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-4">
                    <div class="p-3 bg-blue-500/10 rounded-xl text-blue-500">
                        <i class="fas fa-server text-xl"></i>
                    </div>
                    <span class="text-[10px] font-bold text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-tighter">Live Data</span>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-slate-400 text-sm font-medium uppercase tracking-wider">Serveurs</h3>
                <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mt-1"><%= stats?.guilds || 0 %></p>
            </div>

            <div class="card-glass p-6 rounded-2xl">
                <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-4">
                    <div class="p-3 bg-purple-500/10 rounded-xl text-purple-500">
                        <i class="fas fa-users text-xl"></i>
                    </div>
                    <span class="text-[10px] font-bold text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-tighter">Engagement</span>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-slate-400 text-sm font-medium uppercase tracking-wider">Utilisateurs</h3>
                <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mt-1"><%= stats?.users || 0 %></p>
            </div>

            <div class="card-glass p-6 rounded-2xl">
                <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-4">
                    <div class="p-3 bg-yellow-500/10 rounded-xl text-yellow-500">
                        <i class="fas fa-coins text-xl"></i>
                    </div>
                    <span class="text-[10px] font-bold text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-tighter">Currency</span>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-slate-400 text-sm font-medium uppercase tracking-wider">Masse Monétaire</h3>
                <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mt-1"><%= stats?.economy?.totalBalance || 0 %> <span class="text-sm text-slate-500">coins</span></p>
            </div>

            <div class="card-glass p-6 rounded-2xl">
                <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-4">
                    <div class="p-3 bg-red-500/10 rounded-xl text-red-500">
                        <i class="fas fa-hammer text-xl"></i>
                    </div>
                    <span class="text-[10px] font-bold text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-tighter">Safety</span>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-slate-400 text-sm font-medium uppercase tracking-wider">Warns Actifs</h3>
                <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mt-1"><%= stats?.warns || 0 %></p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
            
            <div class="lg:col-span-2 space-y-6">
                <div class="bg-slate-900/50 border border-slate-800 rounded-3xl p-8">
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-6 flex items-center gap-3">
                        <i class="fas fa-list-ul text-blue-500"></i> Vos Serveurs
                    </h2>
                    
                    <div class="space-y-4">
                        <div class="p-10 border-2 border-dashed border-slate-800 rounded-2xl text-center">
                            <i class="fas fa-lock text-4xl text-slate-700 mb-4"></i>
                            <p class="text-slate-500 italic">L'authentification OAuth2 est en cours de déploiement.<br>Bientôt, vous verrez ici la liste de vos serveurs administrables.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="space-y-6">
                <div class="card-glass p-6 rounded-3xl">
                    <h3 class="font-bold text-white mb-4 italic tracking-widest uppercase text-xs">System Status</h3>
                    <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm">
                        <li class="flex justify-between border-b border-slate-800 pb-2">
                            <span class="text-slate-500">Latence API</span>
                            <span class="text-green-400 font-mono">PONG ms</span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex justify-between border-b border-slate-800 pb-2">
                            <span class="text-slate-500">Hébergeur</span>
                            <span class="text-slate-300">Render.com</span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex justify-between border-b border-slate-800 pb-2">
                            <span class="text-slate-500">Node Engine</span>
                            <span class="text-slate-300">v18.20.8</span>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-blue-600 rounded-3xl p-6 text-white overflow-hidden relative shadow-blue-500/20 shadow-2xl">
                    <i class="fas fa-bolt absolute -right-4 -bottom-4 text-8xl opacity-20"></i>
                    <h4 class="font-bold text-lg mb-1 italic">Mode BETA v2.0.1</h4>
                    <p class="text-blue-100 text-xs">Le système d'XP a été désactivé pour prioriser la vitesse du panel web.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

    </main>

    <footer class="py-12 text-center text-slate-600 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em]">
        Sentinel Infrastructure &copy; 2026 — Clément DUPONT
    </footer>

</body>
</html>